---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - EIM Research Lab">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-header-content">
        <div class="hero-tag"><span></span> About Us</div>
        <h1>About <span class="text-gradient-red">EIM</span> Research Lab</h1>
        <p class="hero-desc">Getting closer to the Enterprise Infrastructure Management research laboratory at Telkom University.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-overview-grid" style="margin-bottom: 80px;">
        <div class="about-content">
          <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">Enterprise Infrastructure Management Laboratory</h2>
          <p class="hero-desc" style="margin-bottom: 20px; max-width: 100%;">
            EIM (Enterprise Infrastructure Management) is a research laboratory under the S1 Information Systems Study Program, Enterprise and Industrial System Expertise Group, Faculty of Industrial Engineering, Telkom University.
          </p>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 20px;">
            We focus on understanding and developing digital infrastructure such as computer networks, operating systems, cloud computing, and cybersecurity. We conduct research, in-depth studies, and large-scale technology training to prepare future digital talents.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-image" style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
          <img src="/img/Salinan EIM.png" alt="EIM Lab" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-visionmission-grid glass-panel" style="margin-bottom: 80px;">
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 40px;">
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--accent-red); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i> Vision
            </h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6;">
              To establish the Enterprise Infrastructure Management (EIM) Research Laboratory as a hub for optimal assistant potential development, creating a leading, collaborative, and competitive research laboratory capable of producing innovative and professional human resources ready to contribute academically and industrially.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--accent-cyan); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye"></i> Mission
            </h3>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; padding-left: 20px;">
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Strengthening faith and devotion as a moral foundation in every activity of the EIM Research Laboratory.</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Fostering smart, professional, and responsible assistants in academics, research, and community service.</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Creating a conducive and productive laboratory environment by upholding EIM Work values.</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Developing sustainable work programs through innovation and quality improvement.</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Strengthening communication and collaboration with all stakeholders.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Our Values</h2>
          <p>Core values that serve as pillars and work culture in EIM Lab.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="focus-grid">
          <div class="focus-card glass-panel">
            <div class="focus-icon" style="color: var(--accent-red);">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-handshake"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Reliability</h3>
            <p>Building trust through a strong and consistent identity in every research and service.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="focus-card glass-panel">
            <div class="focus-icon">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-award"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Commitment</h3>
            <p>Demonstrating high dedication to creating technology innovations that impact society.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="focus-card glass-panel">
            <div class="focus-icon" style="color: var(--accent-red);">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-people-arrows"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Availability</h3>
            <p>Always present as a platform for collaboration, exchanging ideas, and developing digital science.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="focus-card glass-panel">
            <div class="focus-icon">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Quality</h3>
            <p>Delivering research work, practical solutions, and training with the highest quality standards.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
